Title: An Act Changing the Name of Tupas Street in Davao City to Carlos Enriquez Street
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 677
An Act Changing the Name of Tupas Street in Davao City to Carlos Enriquez Street
Section 1. The street in Danao City, in the island of Cebu, Philippines, now known as Tupas Street, is hereby renamed, and shall be known as Carlos Enriquez Street.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1Ã¢wphi1
Approved: March 7, 1984
